OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with heavy rain
OL,6,Fspreading northeast. Orkney turns dry
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon, but rain
OL,8,Fcontinues in Shetland. Strong winds
OL,9,Ffor Orkney but gales or possibly
OL,10,Fsevere gales for Shetland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain clears Shetland, then a
OL,13,Fdry evening with clear spells,
OL,14,Fespecially for Orkney. Turning
OL,15,Fcloudier overnight with outbreaks of
OL,16,Frain spreading northwards. Strong
OL,17,Fsoutheasterly winds with risk of
OL,18,Fcoastal gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
