OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA mixed day of sunny spells
OL,6,Fand blustery showers, which may be
OL,7,Fheavy at times. Strong southeasterly
OL,8,Fwinds and risk of coastal gales.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,11,For sunny spells with showers on
OL,12,FMonday. Mostly dry with sunny spells
OL,13,Fon Tuesday. Cloudier on Wednesday with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain. Winds becoming
OL,15,Flight then strengthening on Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
